  <brief_title>Clinical Trial of Remote Preconditioning in Patients Undergoing Cervical Decompression Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning on Biochemical Markers and Neurological Outcomes in Patients Undergoing Elective Cervical Decompression Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
